# German Credit Analysis

## Project Overview
This project analyzes German credit scores to determine whether the applicant will make a good or bad credit risk. Goals of this project include:
1. Run 5 data exploration functions
2. Partition into training and validation sets
3. Run Logistic regression
4. Create visualizations

## Tools Used
- R (ggplot2, lattice, caret, gains, rpart, rpart.plot)
- R Studio

## Project Structure

data/: Contains datasets.
scripts/: R scripts for analysis.
images/: Visualizations.
results/: Summary outputs.
